OL,4,CSerra Leone's chimpanzees: The newly
OL,5,Cweds who set up a sanctuary
OL,6, Bala Amarasekaran and his wife,
OL,7, Sharmila, spotted the baby chimpanzee
OL,8, tied to a tree in a village in a rural
OL,9, part of Sierra Leone.
OL,11,FHe was for sale.
OL,13,FThe couple bought the animal and
OL,14,Fpledged to care for him.
OL,16,FLittle did they know that this chance
OL,17,Fencounter would change their lives.
OL,18,FThree decades later, they run a
OL,19,Fsanctuary devoted to saving the
OL,20,Fcritically endangered subspecies known
OL,21,Fas the Western chimpanzee.
